title: Superman - Birthright (2003) (Complete) (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
description:
English | CBR | 6 Issues

Superman: Birthright #1-12 (of 12)
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  September 2003 - September 2004

Writer:  Mark Waid
Penciller:  Leinil Francis Yu
Inker:  Gerry Alanguilan
Colorist:  Dave McCaig
Letterer:  Comic Craft
Cover Artists:  Leinil Francis Yu and Gerry Alanguilan

BIRTHRIGHT updates the Man of Steel's origin, breathing new life into the classic story of the super-powered son of a doomed planet destined to grow up to become the world's greatest protector, Superman! This series marked Mark Waid's return to DC Comics and Leinil Yu's DCU debut!

Thanks goes to Inner Demons for this release.
